x4freetext: Fast pulse reactor IBR-30 in booster
Cylindrical battery of 26 He-3 SNM-18 counters
Metallic Nb, Mo, Pb discs of 50 mm diameter and
thickness 1 mm for Nb, 0.4 mm for Mo, 0.5mm for Pb.
SPA was added in REACTION of Subents 003, 006.
Digitized data were added in Subents .012, .013 .
For background 10% in 4-200 keV energy range,
in lower energy range - up to 70%.
